        <title>Borderless windowed mode support missing</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Cpl.1nsane]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Adding -windowed -noborder to the games launch options works for the moment, give it a whirl.</p>
<p>If you’re unaware of how to add this: right click on black mesa in your steam games list, click properties and the bottom of the list then click the <span class="bbcode-b">Set Launch Options</span> button which will bring up box to add the lines too.</p>
